Package: DupSeqR
Title: Analysis of Duplex Sequencing Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew", "Meier", , "matthew.meier@hc-sc.gc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8199-8754")),
    person("Annette", "Dodge", , "annette.dodge@hc-sc.gc.ca", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0446-9055"))
  )
Description: Standard methods for importing the mutation lists provided
    within a Duplex Sequencing experiment. Provides a set of analytical
    tools for statistical testing and visualization of mutation data;
    comparison to COSMIC and/or germline signatures; etc.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
